"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-18-emmanuel-onwubiko-mixing-olympic-and-politics-is-toxic\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published on By William Earl, a Western journalist, reported how the recently concluded Paris Olympics made history in the area of media viewership.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.152807714056916e-15, \"text\": \"Earl\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 0.9999999968431439, \"rank\": 3.157057196143716e-09, \"text\": \"Western\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}, {\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 115}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 127}, {\"ngram\": \"media viewership\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His piece was published on July 27th.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His piece\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 161}, {\"ngram\": \"July 27th\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wrote that the watery spectacle of the Opening Ceremony of the 2024 Paris Games delivered 28.6 million viewers for NBCUniversal platforms, making it the most-watched kick-off for a summer Olympics since London in 2012.\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998835847, \"rank\": 1.1647799924152323e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999645297, \"rank\": 3.524051549536333e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the watery spectacle\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 272}, {\"ngram\": \"28.6 million viewers\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"a summer Olympics\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hear him: \\\"Last night's Opening Ceremony, one of the most ambitious and complex in Olympic history, was a spectacle for those in attendance in Paris, delivered a huge audience across our NBCU platforms, and set records for Peacock,\\\" said NBC Sports President Rick Cordella.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9998995752455183, \"rank\": 6.658564584994644e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.657280573223645e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1450642248644618e-19, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.995250337311435, \"rank\": 0.004772329478277652, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\", \"score\": 0.992684896232193, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cordella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacle\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"attendance\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge audience\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thanks to the tireless effort of our production and engineering teams, and extensive promotion, we are off to a strong start that is in line with the expectations of our NBC stations, and distribution and advertising partners.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 858, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999998990188084, \"rank\": 1.0090879007521871e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tireless effort\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"our production and engineering teams\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong start\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"distribution and advertising partners\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are in great position as we look forward to the next two weeks of competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great position\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the next two weeks\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The theatrical, four-hour ceremony that aired live on Friday afternoon in the U.S. came in 10 million viewers higher than NBCUniversal's coverage of the Tokyo opening ceremony in 2021 and more than 2 million higher than Rio in 2016, according to NBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998835847, \"rank\": 1.1647799924152323e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.321544909569208e-18, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\", \"score\": 0.9999999892916095, \"rank\": 6.468216369658641e-09, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998835847, \"rank\": 1.1647799924152323e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The theatrical, four-hour ceremony\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday afternoon\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The traditional procession of the national teams from each competing country was done this time via boat down the Seine - and event organizers did not disappoint on the promise of arresting visuals to kick off the event that the nation aims to be a showcase of modern France.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999338444714723, \"rank\": 6.615990538937381e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9878275987935824, \"rank\": 0.009158049775379389, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The traditional procession\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"the national teams\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"each competing country\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"boat\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the promise\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"arresting visuals\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"a showcase\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics also has its bad side globally because of the controversy surrounding the same opening ceremony that attracted so much television viewership.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its bad side\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the same opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"so much television viewership\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy was the decision of the organisers to use LGBTS practitioners to depict the last supper in a way to denigrate one of the highest and most spiritual events in Christendom: the last supper of Jesus Christ.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999407430726, \"rank\": 5.925697935361987e-07, \"text\": \"Christendom\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999992328715266, \"rank\": 7.671290244609312e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The controversy\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTS practitioners\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"the last supper\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest and most spiritual events\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"the last supper\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Locally, the Paris Olympics 2024 has also come with its own Controversy associated with the lackluster performance of team Nigeria which won no medal even after approximately N12 billion was spent on that trip to France for the Olympics by the 86-member strong Nigerian team.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8134285908077022e-29, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9878275987935824, \"rank\": 0.009158049775379389, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999988158379, \"rank\": 1.1845191250916354e-09, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"its own Controversy\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the lackluster performance\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"no medal\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"that trip\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As aforementioned, the recently concluded Paris 2024 Olympics ended with Nigeria facing a bitterly disappointing outcome, marked by a lack of medals despite an investment of approximately 12 billion Naira and a sizable contingent of 82 to 86 athletes.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2269, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8134285908077022e-29, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Naira\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bitterly disappointing outcome\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"an investment\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"a sizable contingent\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"82 to 86 athletes\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics, ranging from political commentators to sports enthusiasts, have been quick to assign blame to the Minister of Sports, Senator John Owan Enoh.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Critics\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"political commentators\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"sports enthusiasts\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"blame\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, such a simplistic attribution of responsibility overlooks the multifaceted challenges and entrenched issues within Nigeria's sports administration.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2723, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8134285908077022e-29, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a simplistic attribution\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"the multifaceted challenges\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"entrenched issues\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complexities of sports management, both at the federal and state levels, reveal that the issues are far deeper than the performance of a single minister.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The complexities\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"sports management\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"the federal and state levels\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"a single minister\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understanding these intricacies is crucial to addressing the root causes of Nigeria's poor showing at the Olympics and charting a path forward for future success.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2990, \"end\": 2997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8134285908077022e-29, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these intricacies\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"the root causes\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"a path\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"future success\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the heart of the criticisms lies a misunderstanding of the role and influence of the Minister of Sports.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"the criticisms\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"a misunderstanding\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3132}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"influence\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3158}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other ministries, where the minister may have near-total control over the operations and outcomes, the sports ministry operates within a complex web of federations and governing bodies.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other ministries\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"near-total control\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"the operations\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"outcomes\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports ministry\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3311}, {\"ngram\": \"a complex web\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"federations\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3356}, {\"ngram\": \"bodies\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The autonomy granted to these federations, including the Nigerian Football Federation (NFF) and others, significantly limits the minister's ability to enact sweeping changes or hold them accountable for performance outcomes.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigerian Football Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The autonomy\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"these federations\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"NFF\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister's ability\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"sweeping changes\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3552}, {\"ngram\": \"performance outcomes\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, the NFF operates independently of the Minister of Sports, and any attempt to dissolve or override the federation could result in severe sanctions from FIFA.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3622, \"end\": 3625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.2407842841436e-12, \"text\": \"NFF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Football_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 3769, \"end\": 3773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.516652771016023e-13, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3616}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3664}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"any attempt\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"the federation\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"severe sanctions\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same autonomy is seen across other sports federations, many of which have been entrenched in their current form for years, making rapid reforms a near impossibility.\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The same autonomy\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports federations\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3832}, {\"ngram\": \"their current form\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"rapid reforms\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Senator Enoh, appointed less than a year ago, is in a position where he must navigate these entrenched structures while attempting to implement change.\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 4097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Senator Enoh\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3958}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4008}, {\"ngram\": \"these entrenched structures\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The expectation that significant reforms and performance improvements could be achieved in such a short period is unrealistic.\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The expectation\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"significant reforms\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4138}, {\"ngram\": \"performance improvements\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4167}, {\"ngram\": \"such a short period\", \"from\": 4189, \"to\": 4208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics fail to recognize that the Minister is constrained by these long-standing structures, which require time and careful strategy to reform.\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Critics\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4232}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"these long-standing structures\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4317}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"careful strategy\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blaming him for the immediate outcomes of the Paris Olympics is not only unjust but also counterproductive, as it distracts from the systemic issues that need to be addressed.\", \"from\": 4370, \"to\": 4545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the immediate outcomes\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"the systemic issues\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the significant criticisms levelled against the Minister has been the omission of Favour Ofili from the 100-meter race.\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4636, \"end\": 4648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\", \"score\": 0.9999688897388217, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Favour Ofili\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the significant criticisms\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4610}, {\"ngram\": \"the omission\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4632}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter race\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision has been widely condemned, with many pointing fingers at the Minister.\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4687}, {\"ngram\": \"many pointing fingers\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it is essential to clarify that the Minister of Sports does not directly handle athlete registrations.\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 4816, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete registrations\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The responsibility for athlete selection and registration lies with the Nigeria Olympic Committee (NOC) and the Athletics Federation of Nigeria (AFN), both of which operate independently of the Minister's direct control.\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 5091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4943, \"end\": 4968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigeria Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4970, \"end\": 4973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999911779, \"rank\": 8.816675877578218e-11, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 5016, \"end\": 5019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9999999979763743, \"rank\": 2.0240146953837984e-09, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The responsibility\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete selection\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4911}, {\"ngram\": \"registration\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4928}, {\"ngram\":