alification was due to a technical rule infringement, unrelated to any actions by the Minister.\", \"from\": 5554, \"to\": 5687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disqualification\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"a technical rule infringement\", \"from\": 5615, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"any actions\", \"from\": 5659, \"to\": 5670}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team had previously competed without incident, suggesting that the issue was not a result of the Minister's intervention but rather an unfortunate occurrence that could happen to any team.\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5696}, {\"ngram\": \"incident\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5737}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 5755, \"to\": 5764}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5781}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister's intervention\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 5812}, {\"ngram\": \"an unfortunate occurrence\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"any team\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, this incident has been used by some as further evidence of ministerial failure, a claim that does not hold up under scrutiny.\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 6011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this incident\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5899}, {\"ngram\": \"further evidence\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 5941}, {\"ngram\": \"ministerial failure\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5964}, {\"ngram\": \"a claim\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 5973}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, criticisms regarding athletes' registration and accreditation have not been substantiated beyond the Ofili incident.\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"criticisms\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' registration\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6069}, {\"ngram\": \"accreditation\", \"from\": 6074, \"to\": 6087}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ofili incident\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were no other significant issues reported, and the accreditation process for athletes and coaches proceeded without major problems.\", \"from\": 6143, \"to\": 6280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no other significant issues\", \"from\": 6154, \"to\": 6181}, {\"ngram\": \"the accreditation process\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6221}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6226, \"to\": 6234}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 6239, \"to\": 6246}, {\"ngram\": \"major problems\", \"from\": 6265, \"to\": 6279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This indicates that, contrary to the claims of widespread mismanagement, the process was largely successful, and the issues that did arise were isolated rather than indicative of a broader failure.\", \"from\": 6281, \"to\": 6478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the claims\", \"from\": 6314, \"to\": 6324}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread mismanagement\", \"from\": 6328, \"to\": 6352}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 6354, \"to\": 6365}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 6394, \"to\": 6404}, {\"ngram\": \"a broader failure\", \"from\": 6460, \"to\": 6477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the overall lacklustre performance, there were notable achievements that should not be overshadowed by the medal count.\", \"from\": 6480, \"to\": 6607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overall lacklustre performance\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"notable achievements\", \"from\": 6535, \"to\": 6555}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal count\", \"from\": 6591, \"to\": 6606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Nigerian women's basketball team, the D'Tigress, showcased exceptional talent and resilience.\", \"from\": 6608, \"to\": 6705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6612, \"end\": 6620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"