 \"from\": 8287, \"to\": 8299}, {\"ngram\": \"financial investment\", \"from\": 8319, \"to\": 8339}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 8365, \"to\": 8372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The challenges facing Nigerian sports are multifaceted and require a comprehensive approach that addresses both the immediate needs of athletes and the long-term development of sports infrastructure.\", \"from\": 8374, \"to\": 8573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8396, \"end\": 8404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999988158379, \"rank\": 1.1845191250916354e-09, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The challenges\", \"from\": 8374, \"to\": 8388}, {\"ngram\": \"a comprehensive approach\", \"from\": 8441, \"to\": 8465}, {\"ngram\": \"both the immediate needs\", \"from\": 8481, \"to\": 8505}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 8509, \"to\": 8517}, {\"ngram\": \"the long-term development\", \"from\": 8522, \"to\": 8547}, {\"ngram\": \"sports infrastructure\", \"from\": 8551, \"to\": 8572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Preparations for the next Olympics should begin immediately.\", \"from\": 8575, \"to\": 8635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Preparations\", \"from\": 8575, \"to\": 8587}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Olympics\", \"from\": 8592, \"to\": 8609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes developing a robust training program, investing in state-of-the-art facilities, and ensuring that athletes have the resources they need to compete at the highest levels.\", \"from\": 8636, \"to\": 8819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a robust training program\", \"from\": 8661, \"to\": 8686}, {\"ngram\": \"the-art\", \"from\": 8710, \"to\": 8717}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 8748, \"to\": 8756}, {\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 8762, \"to\": 8775}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest levels\", \"from